## 8) Header contract (layout docs summary)

**Key variables:** `logo`, `store_name`, `categories` (`name`, `url`, optional `children[]` with `name`, `url`), `announcement_config` (`text` string[], `type`: simple / slider / marquee), `announcement_text`, `cart_count`, `compare_count`, `wishlist_count`, `is_register_active`, `theme_data`.

**SSR:** Initial counts for cart / compare / wishlist should match badge text and `hidden` at SSR time; the client keeps **`#header-cart-count`**, **`#header-compare-count`**, and **`#header-wishlist-count`** in sync on updates (same pattern as cart).

**CSS hooks (examples in docs):** `cart-btn`, `lang-btn`, `register-btn`, `search-btn` — events must still bubble from the interactive control.

**IDs to preserve:**

| ID | Purpose |
|----|---------|
| `header-cart-count` | Cart badge; storefront updates text and `hidden` |
| `header-compare-count` | Compare badge; pair with `compare-click` on parent button |
| `header-wishlist-count` | Inside `<a href="/wishlist">`; no custom event |
| `header-lang-btn`, `header-lang-mobile` | Language controls (hidden if plugin inactive) |
| `header-register`, `header-register-mobile` | Reserved for future storefront features; **current:** `register-btn` + `register-click` |

IDs must be **unique** in the document (one cart badge, one desktop lang control, at most one mobile lang, etc.).

**Events:** `cart-click` on cart control, `lang-click` with `{ bubbles: true, detail: { anchor: this } }` recommended, `register-click` on `register-btn`, `compare-click` on compare control.

**Doc warnings:** Without `cart-click`, the cart drawer won’t open. Without `id="header-cart-count"`, counts won’t sync. Without `compare-click`, the compare modal won’t open from the header.

