## 9) Footer contract (summary)

**Variables:** `logo`, `store_name`, `categories` (`name`, `slug`), `pages` (`title`, `slug`), `social` (`type`, `url`, `label`, `icon`), `year`, `payment_img`, `phone`, `email`, `address`, `has_contact`, `shop_label`, `help_label`, `subscribe_label`, `email_placeholder`, `follow_label`, `rights_label`, `show_powered`, `theme_data`.

**Newsletter form:** class `footer-subscribe-form`, `novalidate`, HTML5 validation (`autocomplete`, `inputmode`, `pattern`, `required`, `aria-required`), trim email, then `CustomEvent('footer-subscribe', { bubbles: true, detail: { email } })` and `this.reset()`.

