## 10) Product sections — quick variable index

### `breadcrumbs.liquid`

`categories` (`name`, `slug`), `product_name`, `home_text`. Internal links use SPA interception. Placement inside product details may follow admin flag `is_breadcrumbs_in_details`.

### `gallery.liquid`

`images[]`, `mainImage`, `product_name`, `theme_data`. Video: `contains '.mp4'`. Thumbnail / swipe behavior is local Liquid + `script.js` unless the parent re-renders variant data. No custom events to the app.

### `product-details.liquid`

`product_name`, `price`, `sale_price`, `currency`, `rating`, `reviews_count`, `description` (when `is_description_in_details`), `theme_data`, **`product_id`** for wishlist / compare (must match storefront product id).

Events: `toggle-wishlist`, `toggle-compare` with `detail: { productId: '{{ product_id }}' }`.

### `product-description.liquid`

`description` (HTML), `description_label`, `policies[]` (`icon`, `title`, `content`), `theme_data`. Optional merge into details per `is_description_in_details`. Accordion vs tabs is theme-defined.

### `fixed-buy-button.liquid`

`product_name`, `price`, `sale_price`, `currency`, `thumb`, `buy_now_text`, `quantity`, `disabled`, `hide_quantity`, `increase_disabled`, `theme_data`.

Required events with `bubbles: true`: `buy-now`, `increment-quantity`, `decrement-quantity`.

### `reviews.liquid`

`reviews[]` (`rating`, `user_name`, `comment`, `image`), `reviews_count`, `average_rating`, `average_rating_display`, `t_users_reviews`, `t_reviews`, `t_share_your_review`, `t_no_reviews`, `theme_data`.

Open modal: `data-review-open` on the button, or dispatch `review-open` per events reference.

### `related-products.liquid`

Same product contract as homepage listings: `products`, `category`, `section_title`, `currency`, `add`, `shop_now`, `sale`, `theme_data`. Shown when the product is not `hide_related_products` and has a category; storefront typically passes up to ~5 products.

**Events:** `quick-add`, `quick-view` only (horizontal scroll recommended).

---

## 11) Home sections — summary

### `slider.liquid`

`slides[]`: `image`, `mobile_image` (optional, ≤425px), `url`, `alt`. If `url` is blank, use `<div>` not `<a>`. Use `<picture>` + `<source media>`. First slide `loading="eager"`, rest `lazy`. Docs suggest `alt="{{ slide.alt | default: 'Slide image' }}"`.

### `categories.liquid`

`categories[]`: `name`, `slug`, `thumb`. Section may present as grid or carousel; links go to `/collections/{{ slug }}`.

### `featured-products.liquid` / `list-products.liquid` / `home-products-grid.liquid`

`products[]`, `category`, `section_title`, `currency`, `add`, `shop_now`, `sale`, `hide_view_all`, `theme_data`.

**Product shape:** `id`, `name`, `slug`, `price`, `sale_price`, `thumb`, `images[]`, `variations[]` (`type`, `props[]` with `name`, `value` for swatches).

**Events:** `quick-add`, `quick-view`, `toggle-wishlist`, `toggle-compare` with `productId`.

### `products-grid.liquid` (search & collections)

Same product contract; `hide_view_all` is always `true` here. The **Load more** button is rendered **outside** Liquid by React; each fetch re-renders this template with the **accumulated** product list.

### Prestig: `promo-countdown-hero` (`theme/home-sections/promo-countdown-hero/`)

Full-width promo hero modeled after layered lifestyle photography: gradient overlay (`overlay_strength` 0–100), left column for eyebrow (**kicker**), **headline**, **description**, and a solid CTA (**cta_label** / **cta_url**). Optional horizontal countdown on the opposite side (**show_countdown**).

| Merchant concern | Setting / mechanism |
|------------------|---------------------|
| Background | **image** URL (defaults to Prestig demo asset); optional **mobile_image** for smaller viewports (`background-image`, `cover`; desktop uses **`image`** again at `min-width: 768px`). **bg_position** controls focal point (`center`, `center right`, `center left`). |
| Typography & contrast | **text_color** for headline, description, countdown digits/labels; **kicker_color** for the eyebrow (falls back to **text_color**). Darkening is from the overlay, not replacing product palette slots. Use **palette**/`theme_data` on other pages as usual. |
| CTA look | **button_bg** and **button_text** (defaults: white / near-black) read as CSS variables on `.promo-countdown-hero__btn`. |
| Countdown modes | **`countdown_mode`**: **`calendar_day`** uses **`countdown_end_date`** (`data-pch-mode="calendar"`, **`data-end`**) — **day–month–year**, end-of-local-day (see **`parsePromoCountdownEndMs`**). **`rolling_hours`** uses **`rolling_duration_hours`**, **`data-pch-mode="rolling"`**, **`data-hours`**, **`data-storage-key`** — **fake urgency** persisted in **`localStorage`** (`pch-promo-roll-{key}-h{N}` like PDP **`fake-counter`**). Only **one** mode renders; picking mode is **`select`**, mutually exclusive fields in admin messaging. |
| Client JS | **`initPromoCountdownHeroTimers()`** calendar; **`initPromoCountdownHeroRollingTimers()`** rolling. Observer attributes: **`data-end`**, **`data-hours`**, **`data-pch-mode`**, **`data-storage-key`**. |

**Distinction:** Platform **`sections/fake-counter.liquid`** stays for **product** PDP. **`promo-countdown-hero`** **`rolling_hours`** mirrors that behaviour **on the homepage** with a customizable storage key (`rolling_storage_key`).

### Prestig: `product-compare-slider` (`theme/home-sections/product-compare-slider/`)

قبل/بعد بصورة واحدة للفرق بين لونين أو منتجين: **`image_left_url`** (طبقة علوية مُقصّة من اليمين)، **`image_right_url`** كخلفية كاملة جهة اليمنى. هيد **eyebrow** + **heading**، أسفل الصورة تعليقات **caption_left/right** مع روابط. **`initial_split_percent`** يضبط المحبب الأولي؛ **`initPrestigeProductCompareSliders()`** يحدّث **`--psc-split`** عن طريق **`pointer`** على `.psc-compare__media`.

