## 13) Performance & a11y (from official examples)

- Slider images: **eager** first slide, **lazy** the rest.
- Gallery / slides: meaningful **alt** from `product_name` or `slide.alt`.
- Video in gallery: `playsinline` / `preload="metadata"` where appropriate.
- Newsletter inputs: `autocomplete`, `inputmode`, `pattern`, `required`, `aria-required`.
- **iOS Safari:** keep real text **input/textarea** font-size at least **~16px** on focus to reduce auto-zoom.

---

## 14) Event flow (from docs)

```
Liquid template / script.js
  → dispatch CustomEvent({ bubbles: true })
  → bubbles to section container (React)
  → useLiquidEvents / app handlers
```

When adding interactions: **do not invent new event names** — stick to the table above or the current platform docs.

